(II) AN EMPLOYEE OF THE OFFICE OF A SHERIFF OF A COUNTY
OR BALTIMORE CITY;
SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
October 1, 2025.
Approved by the Governor, April 22, 2025.
